title.narrative: Judicial Performance Enhancement for Service to Citizen Project ("Mahkamati")

description.narrative: The Project Development Objective is to strengthen the capacity of the Borrower’s justice sector to deliver efficient, timely and transparent services to citizens and businesses through: (a) piloting of a participatory reform process involving judges, administrative staff, judicial auxiliaries and users in selected courts in the Project Area; and (b) strengthening the institutional capacity of the central functions of the MdJL to better support and monitor the court system.
